        <description>This field will store the Account that was identified as matching the Lead record prior to converting into an Opportunity. It will store a value only if the Opportunity is created from Lead Conversion AND the Lead record converted had a Matching Account identified by system logic. It is used to set the Opportunity Owner as the same Owner of the Lead Matching Account in that scenario only.</description>
